					<description><![CDATA[Thank you for this article. His book seems to point in the right direction. The word talented and similar words are often used as an excuse. He&#039;s talented I could never do this. He was born that way we could not get the muscles he got. The fact is that the people who reach the things you dream of often invest more time than you do and therefore they are getting better. The following example explains it:&quot; Robert and Jule never played golf before so they decide train for one month and then they would compete. Robert is training 1 hour and Jule is training 3 hours a day. Jule rules the competition and all the spectator are talking about her phenomenal talent but nobody mentions her effort.&quot;]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Thank you for this article. His book seems to point in the right direction. The word talented and similar words are often used as an excuse. He&#8217;s talented I could never do this. He was born that way we could not get the muscles he got. The fact is that the people who reach the things you dream of often invest more time than you do and therefore they are getting better. The following example explains it:&#8221; Robert and Jule never played golf before so they decide train for one month and then they would compete. Robert is training 1 hour and Jule is training 3 hours a day. Jule rules the competition and all the spectator are talking about her phenomenal talent but nobody mentions her effort.&#8221;</p>
