					<description><![CDATA[In reply to &lt;a href=&quot;https://jamesclear.vercel.app/jerry-rice#comment-8311&quot;&gt;Kim&lt;/a&gt;.

Yes, I&#039;ve felt frequent frustration at not becoming all I could be, because I do nearly all of the childcare, as well as the care of an elderly parent. Typical female role, while working 55 hour weeks, in the middle of the night, weekends, to keep up.  It is not fair, indeed.

But I come to James Clears&#039; blog exactly BECAUSE I must find a way to efficiently be terrific at what I do with the woefully little time I have left to develop my life after caring for everyone else.  My takeaway with today&#039;s blog is this:  I don&#039;t have the &quot;strength&quot; of time to myself, or an old boy&#039;s network, or even always enough confidence in my gifts, like some cocky young males I&#039;ve trained. :-)

But I have some serious talents to offer, and my time and energy is best used to focus on those. Exactly because I have some challenges or disadvantages in other areas that I best not lose energy on from day to day.]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>In reply to <a href="https://jamesclear.vercel.app/jerry-rice#comment-8311">Kim</a>.</p>
<p>Yes, I&#8217;ve felt frequent frustration at not becoming all I could be, because I do nearly all of the childcare, as well as the care of an elderly parent. Typical female role, while working 55 hour weeks, in the middle of the night, weekends, to keep up.  It is not fair, indeed.</p>
<p>But I come to James Clears&#8217; blog exactly BECAUSE I must find a way to efficiently be terrific at what I do with the woefully little time I have left to develop my life after caring for everyone else.  My takeaway with today&#8217;s blog is this:  I don&#8217;t have the &#8220;strength&#8221; of time to myself, or an old boy&#8217;s network, or even always enough confidence in my gifts, like some cocky young males I&#8217;ve trained. :-)</p>
<p>But I have some serious talents to offer, and my time and energy is best used to focus on those. Exactly because I have some challenges or disadvantages in other areas that I best not lose energy on from day to day.</p>
